Australian Energy Minister Says ‘Era of Cheap Energy Is Over’

-- B y   J a m i e   P a t o n
-- 
2011-05-04T03:05:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-04/australian-energy-minister-says-era-of-cheap-energy-is-over-.html
Australian Resources Minister Martin Ferguson said the nation is “fast approaching” a period of
significant energy reform and plans to release a draft of a
“white paper” on the issue by the end of the year.  The report will focus on maintaining energy security,
maximizing  Australia ’s resources, addressing looming skills
shortages and promoting clean power, Ferguson said in a speech
in Sydney today.  To contact the reporters on this story:
